 Travis Lanham\n| editors             = '''Editor''' <br> Jordan D. White <br> '''Assistant Editor''' <br> Annalise Bissa <br> '''Head of X''' <br> [[Jonathan Hickman]]\n|main_char_team=[[Armor (comics)|Armor]]<br>[[Tabitha Smith|Boom Boom]]<br>[[Cannonball (comics)|Cannonball]]<br/>[[Chamber (comics)|Chamber]]<br/>[[Cypher (comics)|Cypher]]<br>[[Glob Herman|Glob]]<br>[[Karma (comics)|Karma]]<br />[[Magik (Illyana Rasputin)|Magik]]<br>[[Magma (comics)|Magma]]<br />Maxime<br/>Manon<br>[[Danielle Moonstar|Mirage]]<br />[[Mondo (comics)|Mondo]]<br/>[[Sunspot (comics)|Sunspot]]<br />[[Wolfsbane (comics)|Wolfsbane]]\n}}\n\n''New Mutants'' was relaunched in November 2019 as part of [[Dawn of X]]. Written by [[Jonathan Hickman]] and Ed Brisson, and drawn by Rod Reis, the initial team comprised [[Chamber (comics)|Chamber]], [[Cypher (comics)|Cypher]], [[Karma (comics)|Karma]], [[Magik (Illyana Rasputin)|Magik]], [[Danielle Moonstar|Mirage]], [[Mondo (comics)|Mondo]], [[Sunspot (comics)|Sunspot]] and [[Wolfsbane (comics)|Wolfsbane]].<ref>[https://www.marvel.com/comics/issue/76757/new_mutants_2019_1 ''New Mutants'' (2019) #1]</ref> A second team comprising [[Armor (comics)|Armor]], [[Tabitha Smith|Boom Boom]], [[Glob Herman|Glob]], Maxime and Manon debuted in issue #3 (December 2019).<ref>[https://www.marvel.com/comics/issue/76759/new_mutants_2019_3 ''New Mutants'' (2019) #3]</ref>\n\n===Volume 4 cast===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|+New Mutants cast\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" | Issues\n! scope=\"col\" | Characters\n|-\n| #1\n| {{hlist|[[Chamber (comics)|Chamber]]|[[Cypher (comics)|Cypher]]|[[Karma (comics)|Karma]]|[[Magik (Illyana Rasputin)|Magik]]|[[Danielle Moonstar|Mirage]]|[[Mondo (comics)|Mondo]]|[[Sunspot (comics)|Sunspot]]|[[Wolfsbane (comics)|Wolfsbane]]}}\n|-\n| #2, 5, 7\n| {{hlist|[[Cannonball (comics)|Cannonball]]|Chamber|Cypher|Karma|Magik|Mirage|Mondo|Sunspot|Wolfsbane}}\n|-\n| #3\u20134, 6\n| {{hlist|[[Angel Salvadore|Angel]]|[[Armor (comics)|Armor]]|[[Barnell Bohusk|Beak]]|[[Tabitha Smith|Boom Boom]]|[[Glob Herman|Glob]]|Manon|Maxime}}\n|-\n| #8\n| {{hlist|Armor|Boom Boom|[[Magma (comics)|Magma]]|Manon|Maxime}}\n|-\n| #9\n| {{hlist|Armor|Boom Boom|Chamber|Cypher|Karma|Magik|Magma|Mirage|Mondo|Wolfsbane}}\n|-\n| #10\n| {{hlist|Armor|Boom Boom|Chamber|Cypher|Glob|Karma|Magik|Magma|Mirage|Mondo|Wolfsbane}}\n|-\n| #11\n| {{hlist|Armor|Boom Boom|Chamber|Cypher|Glob|Karma|Magik|Magma|Manon|Maxime|Mirage|Mondo|Wolfsbane}}\n|-\n| #12\n| {{hlist|Glob|Magik|Mirage|Trinary}}\n|}\n\n===Volume 4 issues===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+Reception of issues of ''New Mutants'' volume 4\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Issue'''\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Publication Date'''\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Writer(s)'''\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Artist'''\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Colorist'''\n! scope=\"col\"| '''[[Comic Book Roundup]] rating'''<ref>{{cite web|url=https://comicbookroundup.com/comic-books/reviews/marvel-comics/new-mutants-(2019)|title=New Mutants (2019) Comic Series Reviews at ComicBookRoundUp.com|publisher=[[Comic Book Roundup]]|accessdate=2020-02-20}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\"| '''Estimated sales to North American retailers (first month)'''\n|-\n| #1\n| November 6, 2019\n| Jonathan Hickman & Ed Brisson\n| colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"| Rod Reis\n| '''8.4''' by 25 professional critics\n| 138,484<ref name=\"Nov19sales\">{{cite web|url=https://www.comichron.com/monthlycomicssales/2019/2019-11.html|title=November 2019 Comic Book Sales to Comics Shops|publisher=Comichron|accessdate=2020-01-22}}</ref>\n|-\n| #2\n| November 27, 2019\n| Jonathan Hickman\n| '''8.9''' by 14 professional critics\n| 60,518<ref name=\"Nov19sales\"/>\n|-\n| #3\n| December 11, 2019\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Ed Brisson\n| Flaviano\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Carlos Lopez\n| '''7.6''' by 14 professional critics\n| 49,991<ref name=\"Dec19sales\">{{cite web|url=https://www.comichron.com/monthlycomicssales/2019/2019-12.html|ti